### ===============================================
### SETUP: Assign incident to technician first
### ===============================================

### Login as Supervisor
POST {{apiBase}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "supervisor@rim.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

# Copy token to @tokenSupervisor

### Assign INC-2025-0001 to technician (ID: 5)
POST {{apiBase}}/incidents/INC-2025-0001/assign
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenSupervisor}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "technicianId": 5
}

# Expected: 200 OK
# Status: OPEN → ASSIGNED

### ===============================================
### 1. Login as Technician
### ===============================================
POST {{apiBase}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "technician@rim.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

# Copy access_token to @tokenTechnician

### ===============================================
### 2. View All Incidents (Should see ONLY my incidents ✅)
### ===============================================
GET {{apiBase}}/incidents
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenTechnician}}

# Expected: 200 OK
# ⚠️ CRITICAL: Should see ONLY incidents assigned to me
# Should NOT see incidents assigned to others or unassigned

### ===============================================
### 3. View Incident Details
### ===============================================
GET {{apiBase}}/incidents/INC-2025-0001
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenTechnician}}

# Expected: 200 OK
# Should see: status = ASSIGNED
# Should see: assigneeId = 5

### ===============================================
### 4. Accept Incident (PRIMARY FUNCTION!) ⭐
### ===============================================
POST {{apiBase}}/incidents/INC-2025-0001/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenTechnician}}

# Expected: 200 OK
# Status should change: ASSIGNED → IN_PROGRESS
# Should set: acceptedAt timestamp

### ===============================================
### 5. Check Status After Accept
### ===============================================
GET {{apiBase}}/incidents/INC-2025-0001
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenTechnician}}

# Expected: 200 OK
# Verify:
# - status: "IN_PROGRESS"
# - acceptedAt: timestamp exists

### ===============================================
### 6. Resolve Incident (PRIMARY FUNCTION!) ⭐⭐⭐
### ===============================================
POST {{apiBase}}/incidents/INC-2025-0001/resolve
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenTechnician}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resolutionNote": "Fixed printer paper jam. Cleaned rollers and replaced worn paper tray. Tested with 20 print jobs successfully."
}

# Expected: 200 OK
# Status should change: IN_PROGRESS → RESOLVED
# Should set: resolvedAt timestamp
# Should save: resolutionNote

### ===============================================
### 7. Check Status After Resolve
### ===============================================
GET {{apiBase}}/incidents/INC-2025-0001
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenTechnician}}

# Expected: 200 OK
# Verify:
# - status: "RESOLVED"
# - resolvedAt: timestamp exists
# - resolutionNote: saved correctly

### ===============================================
### 8. View Statistics (Should see only MY stats)
### ===============================================
GET {{apiBase}}/incidents/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenTechnician}}

# Expected: 200 OK
# Should show ONLY my incidents stats
# NOT all incidents

### ===============================================
### 9. Create Incident (Should Fail ❌)
### ===============================================
POST {{apiBase}}/incidents
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenTechnician}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Incident",
  "description": "Should fail",
  "category": "Hardware",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "storeId": 1
}

# Expected: 403 Forbidden
# Only HELP_DESK and END_USER can create

### ===============================================
### 10. Assign Incident (Should Fail ❌)
### ===============================================
POST {{apiBase}}/incidents/INC-2025-0003/assign
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenTechnician}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "technicianId": 5
}

# Expected: 403 Forbidden
# Only SUPERVISOR, IT_MANAGER, HELP_DESK can assign

### ===============================================
### 11. Close Incident (Should Fail ❌)
### ===============================================
POST {{apiBase}}/incidents/INC-2025-0001/close
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenTechnician}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resolutionNote": "Should fail",
  "photoEvidence": "test.jpg"
}

# Expected: 403 Forbidden
# Only HELP_DESK can close

### ===============================================
### 12. Try to View Other's Incident (Should Fail ❌)
### ===============================================
GET {{apiBase}}/incidents/INC-2025-0003
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenTechnician}}

# Expected: 403 Forbidden (if not assigned to me)
# OR 200 OK (if assigned to me)
# TECHNICIAN can only view their own incidents

### ===============================================
### SUMMARY - Expected Results
### ===============================================

# TECHNICIAN CAN DO (Should return 200 OK):
# ✅ View MY assigned incidents ONLY
# ✅ View MY incident details
# ✅ View MY statistics
# ✅ Accept MY incidents (ASSIGNED → IN_PROGRESS)
# ✅ Resolve MY incidents (IN_PROGRESS → RESOLVED)

# TECHNICIAN CANNOT DO (Should return 403 Forbidden):
# ❌ View ALL incidents (only see mine)
# ❌ View other's incidents
# ❌ Create incidents
# ❌ Assign incidents
# ❌ Close incidents

### ===============================================
### Testing Checklist
### ===============================================

# Setup:
# □ Supervisor assigns incident to technician

# Core Functions:
# □ Login successful (got token)
# □ View ONLY my incidents (not all)
# □ Accept incident works (200 OK) ← Main function!
# □ Status changes: ASSIGNED → IN_PROGRESS
# □ Resolve incident works (200 OK) ← Main function!
# □ Status changes: IN_PROGRESS → RESOLVED
# □ Resolution note saved correctly

# Restrictions:
# □ Cannot create incidents (403)
# □ Cannot assign incidents (403)
# □ Cannot close incidents (403)
# □ Cannot view other's incidents (403)

# Statistics:
# □ Statistics show only MY incidents

### ===============================================
### If All Tests Pass: ✅ TECHNICIAN Role Complete!
### ===============================================
